The proposals can be made on the website www.firmaroku.cz. Afterwards, the organizer of the contest chooses seven candidates for the "anti-award" and, during October, allows the public to vote on the Internet through www.firmaroku.cz/absurdita and www.ihned.cz.
Earn the nonsense that gets the most votes.
